      • execute

        public final void execute(Environment env,
           boolean dispatch,
           Action action,
           java.lang.Object... parameters)
        Schedules to execute an action and waits for it to finish. Prints out what action is executed into output specified by either NON_QUEUE_ACTION_OUTPUT or QUEUE_ACTION_OUTPUT depending whether the action is called on queue or not. No output provided for nested actions - only the top level ones are printed.
        Specified by:
        execute in interface ActionExecutor
        Parameters:
        env - Environment.
        dispatch - if true the action is executed on UI system dispatch thread. This is usually necessary to invoke methods of the UI to get the correct state or to update it.
        action - Action to execute.
        parameters - Parameters to pass to action.run() method.
        See Also:
        TestOut#getOutput(java.lang.String)

      • executeDetached

        public final void executeDetached(Environment env,
                   boolean dispatch,
                   Action action,
                   java.lang.Object... parameters)
        Schedules to execute an action and exits immediately. Used to be called DoSomethingNoBlock operations in jemmy2. Prints out what action is executed into output specified by either NON_QUEUE_ACTION_OUTPUT or QUEUE_ACTION_OUTPUT depending whether the action is called on queue or not. No output provided for nested actions - only the top level ones are printed.
        Specified by:
        executeDetached in interface ActionExecutor
        Parameters:
        env - Environment.
        dispatch - if true the action is executed on UI system dispatch thread. This is usually necessary to invoke methods of the UI to get the correct state or to update it.
        action - Action to execute.
        parameters - Parameters to pass to action.run() method.
        See Also:
        TestOut#getOutput(java.lang.String)

      • executeQueue

        public abstract void executeQueue(Environment env,
                Action action,
                java.lang.Object... parameters)
        Schedules to execute an action through the UI system's dispatch thread and waits for the action to be completed. This method is called from execute() method when it is invoked with dispatch argument set to true.
        Parameters:
        env - Environment.
        action - action to execute.
        parameters - parameters to pass to action.run() method.

      • executeQueueDetached

        public abstract void executeQueueDetached(Environment env,
                        Action action,
                        java.lang.Object... parameters)
        Schedules to execute an action through the UI system's dispatch thread and exits immediately. This method is called from executeDetached() method when it is invoked with dispatch argument set to true.
        Parameters:
        env - Environment.
        action - action to execute.
        parameters - parameters to pass to action.run() method.
